text: <@U02618EV1>: Found a really useful article on HTML5 video – <http://www.jwplayer.com/html5/>

attachments.title: The State of HTML5 Video Report - Industry Research | JW Player
attachments.text: The State of HTML5 Video Report is a compilation of research on HTML5 video playback by Jeroen Wijering, creator of the JW Player. It is updated frequently.
attachments.fallback: JW Player: The State of HTML5 Video Report - Industry Research | JW Player

text: They touch on a lot of things, showing what’s supported, what isn’t, and what may soon be, across all major browsers. Dive in and see if anything ends up being useful to you.
